{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/03/11/使用docker安装Jenkins.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"259f8f3b-fb66-5283-b216-98f830db347c","excerpt":"使用 docker 安装 Jenkins 自从成功通过 docker 安装了 strapi，我一下子对安装一切产生了很大兴趣。 通过可以很快安装。 然后访问服务器的 8080 端口，即可安装对应插件，注意，这些插件不能走代理，所以…非常慢…国内还是用 coding.net 吧。","html":"<h1>使用 docker 安装 Jenkins</h1>\n<p>自从成功通过 docker 安装了 strapi，我一下子对安装一切产生了很大兴趣。</p>\n<p>通过<code class=\"language-text\">docker-compose.yaml</code>可以很快安装。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-yaml line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">jenkins</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">restart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> always\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> jenkins/jenkins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>lts\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">container_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gongbaodd<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>jenkins\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">volumes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> ./docker/jenkins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>/home/ubuntu/jenkins_home\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">ports</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"50000:50000\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"8080:8080\"</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然后访问服务器的 8080 端口，即可安装对应插件，注意，这些插件不能走代理，所以…非常慢…国内还是用 coding.net 吧。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/使用docker安装Jenkins.html","date":"March 11, 2020","title":"使用docker安装Jenkins"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/使用docker安装Jenkins.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/应该是目前最好的WSL2和Virtualbox共存的方法了.html","title":"应该是目前最好的WSL2和Virtualbox共存的方法了"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","title":"snap添加代理"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}